(Sample Milling Program - Pocket and Contour)
O0001 (SAMPLE MILLING PROGRAM)
N10 G21 (METRIC UNITS)
N20 G90 G54 (ABSOLUTE POSITIONING, WORK OFFSET 1)
N30 G17 (XY PLANE SELECTION)
N40 G40 G80 G49 (CANCEL COMPENSATION, CYCLES, TOOL OFFSET)
N50 T01 M06 (TOOL CHANGE - 10MM END MILL)
N60 S2500 M03 (SPINDLE ON CW, 2500 RPM)
N70 G00 X0 Y0 Z50.0 (RAPID TO START POSITION)
N80 G43 Z5.0 H01 (TOOL LENGTH COMPENSATION)
N90 M08 (COOLANT ON)

(POCKET MILLING - 50MM x 30MM RECTANGULAR POCKET)
N100 G00 X-30.0 Y-20.0 (POSITION FOR POCKET)
N110 Z5.0 (RAPID TO CLEARANCE HEIGHT)
N120 G01 Z-5.0 F500 (FEED TO CUT DEPTH)
N130 X30.0 F1000 (MILL FIRST PASS)
N140 Y-10.0
N150 X-30.0
N160 Y0.0
N170 X30.0
N180 Y10.0
N190 X-30.0
N200 Y20.0
N210 X30.0
N220 Z5.0 F500 (RETRACT)
N230 G00 Z50.0 (RAPID RETRACT)

(CIRCULAR POCKET MILLING)
N240 G00 X0 Y0 (CENTER POSITION)
N250 Z5.0 (CLEARANCE)
N260 G01 Z-3.0 F500 (FEED TO DEPTH)
N270 G02 X15.0 Y0 I-15.0 J0 F800 (FULL CIRCLE CW)
N280 G03 X-15.0 Y0 I-15.0 J0 (FULL CIRCLE CCW)
N290 G01 X0 Y0
N300 Z5.0 F500 (RETRACT)
N310 G00 Z50.0 (RAPID RETRACT)

(CONTOUR MILLING - PROFILE)
N320 G00 X-40.0 Y-25.0 (START POSITION)
N330 Z5.0 (CLEARANCE)
N340 G01 Z-2.0 F500 (FEED TO DEPTH)
N350 G42 D01 F1000 (CUTTER COMP RIGHT)
N360 X40.0 (RIGHT)
N370 Y25.0 (UP)
N380 X-40.0 (LEFT)
N390 Y-25.0 (DOWN)
N400 G40 (CANCEL CUTTER COMP)
N410 Z5.0 F500 (RETRACT)
N420 G00 Z50.0 (RAPID RETRACT)

(DRILLING CYCLE)
N430 G00 X-20.0 Y-15.0 Z50.0
N440 G99 G81 Z-10.0 R2.0 F200 (PECK DRILL)
N450 X20.0
N460 Y15.0
N470 X-20.0
N480 G80 (CANCEL DRILL CYCLE)

(FINISH PASS)
N490 G00 X-35.0 Y-20.0 Z50.0
N500 Z2.0
N510 G01 Z-2.5 F300
N520 G41 D02 F1500
N530 X35.0
N540 Y20.0
N550 X-35.0
N560 Y-20.0
N570 G40
N580 G00 Z50.0

(PROGRAM END)
N590 M09 (COOLANT OFF)
N600 M05 (SPINDLE OFF)
N610 G49 G80 (CANCEL ALL COMPENSATIONS)
N620 G00 Z100.0 (FINAL RETRACT)
N630 X0 Y0 (RETURN TO ORIGIN)
N640 M30 (PROGRAM END AND REWIND)
